title: [Mac] Warcraft 3 + Exp. The Frozen Throne + Serials (English)
description:
Files:

- Serials.txt
- Warcraft 3 ROC.dmg
- Warcraft 3 TFT.dmg
- War3TFT_121b_English
- TFT Patcher 1xx-122a_enUS

How to Install:

1) Mount "Warcraft 3 ROC.dmg" . 
2) Mount "Warcraft 3 TFT.dmg" and execute "The Frozen Throne Installer".
3) Use  serials from "Serials.txt" file.
4) Install "War3TFT_121b_English" patch first.
5) After, install the last patch "TFT Patcher 1xx-122a_enUS".

I have tested in Mac OS X Leopard (10.5.6) and runs very good.
